text: Ordered the ebiko chicken burger set, the veggies are fresh and it tastes good. Classic wagyu burger is delicious too. Tried the beef cheese fries as well popcorn chicken, tastes wise, they are really yummy. Reason why 3 stars is given, this is ordered via delivery but 1 set of the orders did not come with fries and drinks. I was not refunded too despite numerous times of follow ups. It was not a good experience at all!
Definitely shiok! Tried the classic wagyu burger. Beef patty juicy tasted great. Overall shiok!
The atmosphere and service very fast. The customer service is very polite and the food tatse good
Luzhou-flavor and beef burgers are really delicious. It's the first time I've eaten such a delicious burger.

Ordered 2 sets of the mala burger set without fries for 4.99 each, 1 set was missed out when the number was called but was quickly rectified.
note the dine in area is shared with the next door store.
